msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/scout.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 13 (leather armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 16 (3d8 + 3)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/scout.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 11 (+0) | 14 (+2) | 12 (+1) | 11 (+0) | 13 (+1) | 11 (+0) |   \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/scout.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Nature +4, Perception +5, Stealth +6, Survival +5    \n"
"**Senses** passive Perception 15    \n"
"**Languages** any one language (usually Common)    \n"
"**Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/scout.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Keen Hearing and Sight.** The scout has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) "
"checks that rely on hearing or sight. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/scout.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The scout makes two melee attacks or two ranged attacks.    "
"\n"
"**Shortsword.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Longbow.** _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, ranged 150/600 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/scout.md:29
msgid ""
"### Description Scouts are skilled hunters and trackers who offer their "
"services for a fee. Most hunt wild game, but a few work as bounty hunters, "
"serve as guides, or provide military reconnaissance."
msgstr ""
